headline: F5 to Report First Quarter Fiscal Year 2026 Financial Results
summary: SEATTLE, January 07, 2026--F5, Inc. (NASDAQ: FFIV), the global leader in delivering and securing every app and API, announced it will report its first quarter fiscal year 2026 financial results on Tuesday, January 27, 2026, following the market close. F5 will host a live webcast to discuss its results with investors and analysts beginning at 4:30 p.m. ET on January 27, 2026.
